      "text": "Install the rocker arm (A) and hydraulic tappet (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "The rocker arm must be mounted in such a way that it does not tilt."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. Camshaft Holder/Camshaft Mounting"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "372_5.0_jpn_11582842_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install camshaft holder and camshaft."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "The camshaft holder must be assembled with the arrow pointing toward the cam chain.",
        "Check to make sure that the rocker arm is not tilted after the camshaft is installed."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "The camshaft holder must be assembled with the arrow pointing toward the cam chain."
        },
        {
          "text": "The camshaft holder must be assembled with the arrow pointing toward the cam chain."
        },
        {
          "text": "Check to make sure that the rocker arm is not tilted after the camshaft is installed."
        },
        {
          "text": "Check to make sure that the rocker arm is not tilted after the camshaft is installed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "372_5.0_jpn_11582843_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Lubricate the threads and seat surfaces of the camshaft holder bolts with engine oil and tighten them several times in numerical order. Specified torque － : 8.0N·m (0.82kgf·m)"
    },
    {
